reviews.review_text: Very good show, and excellent recording for the most part. There is some horrible diginoise at one point in the second set, but that's the only real flaw in one of the best AUD tapes I've heard lately.

Too many Choco-Espresso beans! My first experience w/ these actually night before....These were fun shows, although I believe a kid got killed by a cop in the parking lot after this night. I'm a Man is worth the listen. Pretty hot!
